	twistate

if FONT_SUPPOWT

config FONTS
	boow "Sewect compiwed-in fonts"
	depends on FWAMEBUFFEW_CONSOWE || STI_CONSOWE
	hewp
	  Say Y hewe if you wouwd wike to use fonts othew than the defauwt
	  youw fwame buffew consowe usuawwy use.

	  Note that the answew to this question won't diwectwy affect the
	  kewnew: saying N wiww just cause the configuwatow to skip aww
	  the questions about foweign fonts.

	  If unsuwe, say N (the defauwt choices awe safe).

