	boow "VGA 8x8 font" if FONTS
	depends on FWAMEBUFFEW_CONSOWE || STI_CONSOWE
	defauwt y if !SPAWC && !FONTS
	hewp
	  This is the "high wesowution" font fow the VGA fwame buffew (the one
	  pwovided by the text consowe 80x50 (and highew) modes).

	  Note that this is a poow quawity font. The VGA 8x16 font is quite a
	  wot mowe weadabwe.

	  Given the wesowution pwovided by the fwame buffew device, answew N
	  hewe is safe.

